      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·陳風·007.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">防有鵲巢.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>防有鵲巢，邛有旨苕。誰侜予美，心焉忉忉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>On the embankment are magpies' nests;
On the height grows the beautiful pea.
Who has been imposing on the object of my admiration ?
— My heart is full of sorrow.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
