      <prop type="x-translation-ref">防有鵲巢.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>中唐有甓，邛有旨鷊。誰侜予美，心焉惕惕。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The middle path of the temple is covered with its tiles;
On the height is the beautiful medallion plant.
Who has been imposing on the object of my admiration?
— My heart is full of trouble.</seg>
      </tuv>
